bel: Parlophone\n* Formats: 11\u00d7CD, 13\u00d7LP, DD\n| 19 || \u2014 || 59 || 24 || 76 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 151<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/music/david-bowie/chart-history/billboard-200/5|title=David Bowie Chart History|website=billboard.com}}</ref>\n|\n*\n|-\n\n! scope=\"row\" |''[[Loving the Alien (1983\u20131988)]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.davidbowie.com/blog/2018/7/18/david-bowie-loving-the-alien-1983-1988-due-october|title=David Bowie Loving The Alien (1983\u20131988) due October|date=July 17, 2018|website=davidbowie.com}}</ref>\n|\n* Released: 12 October 2018\n* Label: Parlophone\n* Formats: 11\u00d7CD, 15\u00d7LP, DD\n| 19 ||\u2014\n| 48 || 18 ||\u2014\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n| \u2014\n|\n*\n|-\n| colspan=\"11\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:8pt;\" | \"\u2014\" denotes items which were not released in that country or failed to chart.\n|-\n| colspan=\"11\" style=\"text-align:left; font-size:10pt;\" | Notes<br />\n{{refbegin}}\n* '''a''' {{Note|note_sound_a}} UK chart position for ''Sound + Vision'' is for the 2014 reissue.\n{{refend}}\n|}\n\n==Soundtracks==\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\" border=\"1\"\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:17em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:17em;\"| Album details\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"2\"| Peak chart<br>positions\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| UK<br/><ref name=\"UK charts\"/>\n\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| AUT<br/><ref name=\"austrian charts\"/>\n|-\n\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Christiane F. (album)|Christiane F.]]''\n|\n* Released: April 1981\n* Label: RCA\n* Formats: LP\n| \u2014 || 3\n|-\n\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Labyrinth (David Bowie album)|Labyrinth]]''<br><small>(with [[Trevor Jones (composer)|Trevor Jones]])</small>\n|\n* Released: 23 June 1986\n* Label: EMI\n* Formats: LP\n| 38<br/><ref>Pegg, p. 381</ref> || \u2014\n|-\n\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[The Buddha of Suburbia 