. 1|It's No Game (Part 1)]]'''\" [A] {{ref label|note_80s_g|g|}}<br/>\"Fashion\" [B]\n| 7\"\n| x\n| x\n| x\n| x\n| x\n| x\n| x\n| x\n| align=\"left\"| \n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| rowspan=\"4\"| 1981\n| align=\"left\"| \"'''[[Scary Monsters (And Super Creeps) (song)|Scary Monsters (And Super Creeps)]]'''\" <small>[edit]</small> [A 7\"]<br/>\"Because You\u2019re Young\" [B 7\"]<hr/><small>France: \"Scary Monsters (And Super Creeps)\" [full] [A 7\"]<br/>\"Up the Hill Backwards\" [B 7\"]</small><hr/><small>\"Scary Monsters (And Super Creeps)\" [full] [A 12\"] {{ref label|note_80s_h|h|}}<br/>\"Because You\u2019re Young\" [B 12\"]</small>\n| 7\"/<br/>12\"/<br/>[[Compact Cassette|CC]]\n| 20\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| 17\n| \u2014\n| x\n| x\n| align=\"left\"|\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| align=\"left\"| \"'''[[Up the Hill Backwards]]'''\" [A]<br/>\"Crystal Japan\" [B]\n| 7\"/<br/>12\" {{ref label|note_80s_i|i|}}\n| 32\n| x\n| x\n| \u2014\n| x\n| x\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| align=\"left\"|\n| A \u2013 ''Scary Monsters''<br/>B \u2013 Non-album track\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| align=\"left\"| \"'''[[Under Pressure]]'''\" [A]<br/><small>(as [[Queen (band)|Queen]] and David Bowie)</small><br/>\"Soul Brother\" [B]<br/><small>(by Queen)</small>\n| 7\"/<br/>12\" {{ref label|note_80s_j|j|}}\n| 1\n| 6\n| 10\n| 21\n| 2\n| 1\n| 29\n| 7\n| align=\"left\"|\n* BPI: Platinum<ref name=\"bpi certs\" />\n* RIAA: 2xPlatinum<ref name=\"Gold & Platinum \u2013 RIAA\">{{Cite news|url=https://www.riaa.com/gold-platinum/?tab_active=default-award&ar=QUEEN,+DAVID+BOWIE&ti=UNDER+PRESSURE|title=Gold & Platinum \u2013 RIAA|work=RIAA|access-date=2018-05-27|language=en-US}}</ref>\n| Bowie \u2013 Non-album track<br/><small> Queen A \u2013 ''[[Hot Space]]''<br/>Queen B \u2013 Non-album track</small>\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| align=\"left\"| \"'''[[Wild Is the Wind (song)|Wild Is the Wind]]'''\" <small>[album version]</small> [A] {{ref label|note_80s_k|k|}}<br/>\"Golden Years\" <small>[album version]</small> [B]<br/><small>[official retrospective release for ''[[ChangesTwoBowie]]''] {{ref label|note_80s_m|m|}}</small>\n| 7\"/<br/>12\" {{ref label|note_80s_l|l|}}\n| 24\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| 15\n| x\n| x\n| x\n| align=\"left\"|\n| ''Station to Station''\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 1982\n| align=\"left\"| '''''[[Baal (EP)|Baal]]''''' {{ref label|note_80s_n|n|}}<br/>\"Baal\u2019s Hymn\" <small>[Hansa version] </small>[A1]<br/>\"Remembering Marie A.\" <small>[Hansa version]</small> [A2]<br/>\"Ballad of the Adventurers\" <small>[Hansa version]</small> [B1]<br/>\"The Drowned Girl\" <small>[Hansa version]</small> [B2] {{ref label|note_80s_o|o|}}<br/>\"The Dirty Song\" <small>[Hansa version]</small> [B3]\n| 7\"EP/<br/>12\" {{ref label|note_80s_p|p|}}\n| 29\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| align=\"left\"|\n| Non-album tracks\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| align=\"left\"| \"'''[[Cat People (Putting Out Fire)]]'''\" <small>[v1] [edit]</small> [A 7\"] {{ref label|note_80s_q1|q|}}<br/><small>(as David Bowie and [[Giorgio Moroder]])</small><br/>\"Paul's Theme (Jogging Chase)\" [B 7\"]<br/><small>(by Giorgio Moroder)</small><hr/><small>Portugal 7\"A: \"Cat People (Putting Out Fire)\" [v1] [full] {{ref label|note_80s_q2|q|}}</small><hr/><small>\"Cat People (Putting Out Fire)\" [v1] [full] [12\"] {{ref label|note_80s_q3|q|}}<br/>\"Paul's Theme (Jogging Chase)\" [B 12\"]</small><hr/><small>Australia: \"Cat People (Putting Out Fire)\" [v1] [edit] [A 12\"]<br/>\"Cat People (Putting Out Fire)\" [v1] [ext. remix] [B 12\"] {{ref label|note_80s_q4|q|}}</small>\n| 7\"/<br/>12\"\n| 26\n| 15\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| 17\n| \u2014\n| 67\n| 9\n| align=\"left\"|\n| ''[[Cat People (1982 film)|Cat People]]'' soundtrack (Giorgio Moroder)\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| align=\"left\"| \"'''[[Peace on Earth/Little Drummer Boy]]'''\" [A 7\"]<br/><small>(as David Bowie and [[Bing Crosby]])<