roes\"\"\n|''The Concert for New York City''\n| Recorded live at [[The Concert for New York City]] on 20 October 2001\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref>\"[{{Allmusic|class=album|id=r563671|pure_url=yes}} The Concert for New York City > Overview]\". [[Allmusic]]. [[Rovi Corporation]]. Retrieved on 10 March 2009.</ref>\n|-\n|2005\n| \"Scary Monsters (And Super Creeps)\"\n|''ONXRT: Live from the Archives Volume 8''\n|\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref>\"[{{Allmusic|class=album|id=r814906|pure_url=yes}} ONXRT: Live from the Archives, Vol. 8 > Overview]\". [[Allmusic]]. [[Rovi Corporation]]. Retrieved on 11 March 2009.</ref>\n|}\n\n===Guest appearances===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:1em;\" | Year\n! Album\n! Artist\n! Details\n! Ref.\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1972\n|''[[All the Young Dudes (album)|All the Young Dudes]]''\n|[[Mott the Hoople]]\n| Producer, [[saxophone]], writer (\"[[All the Young Dudes (song)|All the Young Dudes]]\")\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref>\"[{{Allmusic|class=album|id=r13546|pure_url=yes}} All the Young Dudes > Overview]\". [[Allmusic]]. [[Rovi Corporation]]. Retrieved on 11 March 2009.</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Transformer (Lou Reed album)|Transformer]]''\n|[[Lou Reed]]\n| Co-producer, backing vocals, acoustic guitar\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref>\"[{{Allmusic|class=album|id=r16370/credits|pure_url=yes}} Transformer > Credits]\". [[Allmusic]]. [[Rovi Corporation]]. Retrieved on 11 March 2009.</ref>\n|-\n| 1973\n|''[[Raw Power]]''\n|[[The Stooges|Iggy & the Stooges]]\n| Co-producer with Iggy Pop, [[Audio mixing (recorded music)|Mixing]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref>\"[{{Allmusic|class=album|id=r41208/credits|pure_url=yes}} Raw Power > Credits]\". [[Allmusic]]. [[Rovi Corporation]]. Retrieved on 11 March 2009.</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 1974\n|''[[Now We Are Six (album)|Now We Are Six]]''\n|[[Steeleye Span]]\n| Saxophone (\"[[To Know Him Is to Love Him]]\")\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref>\"[{{Allmusic|cl