oneliest Guy\" \n* \"Bring Me the Disco King\" \n* \"New Killer Star\" [version 2] \n|\n* Director: Steve Lippman aka FLIP\n* Distributor: Columbia Records. \n* Format: DVD\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | \u2014\n|-\n|-\n| colspan=\"7\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:8pt;\" | \"\u2014\" denotes releases that did not chart. \"x\" denotes single not released in that territory.\n|}\n\n===Live TV films===\n\nLive TV films are concerts staged specifically for TV broadcast.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! class=\"unsortable\" rowspan=\"2\" | Title\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Rec\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Rel\n! class=\"unsortable\" rowspan=\"2\" | Filming\n! class=\"unsortable\" rowspan=\"2\" | Film details\n! colspan=\"2\" | Peak chart<br>positions\n|-\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:3.5em;font-size:75%\" |[[GfK Entertainment|GER<br />Albums<br />Chart]]<br /><ref name=\"german albums\" />\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:3.5em;font-size:75%\" |[[Billboard charts|US<br />Top<br />Music<br />Video]]\n|-\n|'''''[[The 1980 Floor Show]]'''''\n| 1973\n| 1973\n|\n* 18\u201320 October 1973\n* [[Marquee Club]] in Soho, London\n| \n* Broadcast: 16 November 1973; USA [[NBC]] on ''[[The Midnight Special (TV series)|The Midnight Special]]''\n* Unreleased\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | \u2014\n|-\n|'''''[[David Bowie and Friends: A Very Special Birthday Concert]]'''''\n| 1997\n| 1997\n|\n* 9 January 1997\n* Madison Square Gardens, New York, USA\n| \n* Broadcast (pay-per-view): 9 January 1997\n* Unreleased\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | \u2014\n|-\n|'''''[[VH1 Storytellers (David Bowie album)|VH1 Storytellers]]'''''\n| 1999\n| 1999\n|\n* 23 August 1999\n* Manhattan Centre Studios, New York, USA\n| \n* Boradcast: USA VH1 1999\n* Released: 2009\n* Formats: DVD\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | \u2014\n|-\n|