 Go Go\" on 2 November 1969\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref name=\"pegg545\">Pegg, p. 545</ref>\n|-\n| ''40 Jaar Top 40: 1969\u20131970''\n| Various artists\n| A Dutch compilation featuring the live performance of \"Space Oddity\" at the [[Ivor Novello Awards]] on 10 May 1970\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref name=\"pegg545\" />\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2005\n| ''The Nomi Song''\n| [[Klaus Nomi]]\n| Includes footage of Nomi's performance with Bowie on ''[[Saturday Night Live]]'' in 1979\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref name=\"pegg545\" />\n|-\n| ''Dick Cavett: Rock Icons''\n| Various artists\n| An interview and performances of \"1984\", \"Young Americans\" and \"Footstompin'\" from ''[[The Dick Cavett Show]]'' recorded on 2 November 1974\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref name=\"pegg545\" />\n|-\n| 2006\n| ''Burt Sugarman's The Midnight Special: Million Sellers''\n| Various artists\n| Live performance of \"Space Oddity\" from the 1980 Floor Show concerts filmed for [[NBC]]'s ''[[The Midnight Special (TV series)|The Midnight Special]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>\"[http://www.videoservicecorp.com/TV/The-Midnight-Special/Midnight-Special-The-Legendary-Performances-Million-Sellers/ Midnight Special, The: Legendary Performances Million Sellers] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090927104502/http://www.videoservicecorp.com/TV/The-Midnight-Special/Midnight-Special-The-Legendary-Performances-Million-Sellers |date=27 September 2009 }}\". Video Service Corp. Retrieved on 11 March 2009.</ref>\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[Remember That Night]]''\n| [[David Gilmour]]\n| Guest appearance at the [[Royal Albert Hall]] on 29 May 2006 performing \"Arnold Layne\" and \"[[Comfortably Numb]]\"\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>\"[{{Allmusic|class=album|id=r1206035|pure_url=yes}} Remember That Night: Live at the Royal Albert Hall > Overview]\". [[Allmusic]]. [[Rovi Corporation]]. Retrieved on 11 March 2009.</ref>\n|}\n\n==References==\n'''General'''\n{{